      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/content/effects-cloud-computing-open-source-compliance" title="Effects of Cloud Computing on Open-Source Compliance">Effects of Cloud Computing on Open-Source Compliance</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
		By <a href="/users/diana-cooper" title="View user profile.">Diana Cooper</a>&nbsp;<!--|
