<p>
Since the emergence of strong cloud service providers like Amazon Web Services,
Google and Rackspace, software development and deployment is increasingly taking
place in the cloud.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/effects-cloud-computing-open-source-compliance"> more>></a></span></p>
